#this thread.py checks the rmsd between the af2 model and the design model and thread the sequences back to the design model if passes requirements. Change rhe rmsd threshold in the thread.py to tailor needs. See example run commands below:

/software/containers/pyrosetta.sif thread.py --input_directory ../5_colabfold/08_29_2024_d5_OH_unfixed --output_directory 08_29_2024_d5_OH_unfixed --reference_directory ../3_realign/08_22_2024_d5_OH


The designs in the example_outputs folder were the designs that I have ordered and tested experimentally. Among them, the design "HAp_binder_design_010_d5_tube_OH_131_130_592_591_EEDE_17_FM_model45_1-atomized-bb-False_10.32_60.00_61_4_s62e143_3mer_4_fixed.pdb" is the HAp1_C3 design that we report in the manuscript.
